counter-app/
├── app.py           # The main Flask application
├── templates/       # Directory for HTML templates
│   └── index.html   # The HTML page to display the counter
├── requirements.txt # Lists Python dependencies
└── Dockerfile       # Instructions for building the Docker image


Once you've created a folder structure like above, execute by the below

## Docker Instructions

### Building the Docker Image

Navigate to the `counter-app` directory and run the following command:

```bash
docker build -t counter-web-app .


##Troubleshooting steps

while running if you face any issues with docker image step, then try running the below command

-> docker pull #your-iamge

-> docker build ## command ~docker build -t counter-web-app .
